IMPULSIVE SPENDING bobbled at the start and recovered to vie early on inside a pair before being shaken off a bit, gave chase along the rail into and through the turn under coaxing from the three-eighths, spun just off the inside into upper stretch and faltered. BEAR'S CORRECT vied early on from the two path between foes before dueling with WEST STAR, had that rival take over and was shaken off when put to urging three furlongs from home, angled out five to six wide in retreat at the quarter pole and folded in the stretch.

FOR MAIDENS, FILLIES AND MARES THREE YEARS OLD AND UPWARD FOALED IN NEW YORK STATE AND APPROVED BY THE NEW YORK STATE-BRED REGISTRY. Three Year Olds, 118 lbs.; Older, 125 lbs. Claiming Price $25,000 (1.5% Aftercare Assessment Due At Time Of Claim Otherwi se Claim Will Be Void)(If No Three Year Olds Are Entered, Starting Weight Shall Be 122 lbs).
RACE.FOOTNOTES: EVER GRACEFUL coaxed from the gate, chased four then three wide under coaxing from the three-eighths, swung three to four wide for home, dug in under a drive rallying to take command seventy yards from home, then dug in holding safe to the finish under late threat. LA CHANCE coaxed from the start, chased four wide under coaxing from the three-eighths, swung five wide for home and closed well to latch on the winner as she hit the wire. TUMBLES brushed the near side stall at the start, chased three then two wide under coaxing from the three-eighths, angled six wide into upper stretch and kicked on belatedly to the finish. STORMY'S IN STYLE coaxed from the gate, chased three wide under coaxing from the five-sixteenths, had first run at the leader through the stretch and was heads apart for the front when the eventual winner took over seventy yards from home, ran on to preserve the last major share. MRS BELL chased just off the inside until tucked inside through the turn coming under coaxing at the five-sixteenths, took the inside route into upper stretch, stayed on one paced to the finish but was outkicked. GEORGIE'S LADIES broke in at the start, prompted the leader from the outside in the four path down the backstretch before advancing tucked to the two path into the turn, took over command with seven-sixteenths to go, shook away and took the inside route into upper stretch, dug in under threat and was caught seventy yards from home and weakened in the late stages. BUSTINROXY hustled from the gate, showed the way early on from the two path under some pressure to the outside, tucked inside into the turn and yielded the front at the seven-sixteenths, spun just off the inside into upper stretch and weakened. GRACE IN MOTION chased along the inside down the backstretch and then just off the inside through the turn under coaxing from the three-eighths, went seven wide into upper stretch and made no headway. MADAME ROSE got off in a tangle bucking at the start, chased five to six paths off the inside down the backstretch and then four wide through the turn, angled in and spun just off the inside into upper stretch and was eased home to the finish, then got pulled up after the finish and was subsequently vanned off.
